<bibRefCitation author="Peck, S. B." box="[771,919,1797,1823]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" pagination="179 - 186" refId="ref103955" refString="Peck, S. B. (1999 c) A review of the Dissochaetus (Coleoptera: Leiodidae; Cholevinae) of the United States and Canada. Cana- dian Entomologist, 131, 179 - 186. https: // doi. org / 10.4039 / Ent 131179 - 2" type="journal article" year="1999">Peck (1999c)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Peck, S. B. &amp; Cook, J." box="[974,1200,1797,1823]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" pagination="1 - 76" refId="ref104390" refString="Peck, S. B. &amp; Cook, J. (2014) A review of the small carrion beetles and the round fungus beetles of the West Indies (Coleoptera: Leiodidae), with descriptions of two new genera and 61 new species. Insecta Mundi, 0397, 1 - 76." type="book chapter" year="2014">Peck &amp; Cook (2014</bibRefCitation>
